Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
Of course it is bad thing. You can not force the students to do something. Of course, you have your condideration, such as you want students from different countries to get to know each other. But anyway, it is not a good idea to force them to do so. Or maybe you can provide free dorms?